&lt;p&gt;本功能基于  &lt;code&gt;markdown-it-emoji&lt;/code&gt;  ，所有标签参考&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL21hcmtkb3duLWl0L21hcmtkb3duLWl0LWVtb2ppL2Jsb2IvbWFzdGVyL2xpYi9kYXRhL2Z1bGwuanNvbg==&#34;&gt;戳此&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
